; font-size: 16px;"&gt;埃马纽埃尔·马克龙(Emmanuel Macron)总统任期的&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;最后预算摊牌&lt;/strong&gt;已经准备好成为法国十年来&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/T2dHGQpStc4nCbf90a765EY55h9tXwQYSDfU-orLYhpQPiQRxasAqfr4S9tcu_v5TX37Ui1cWoVzI8mkoyu4KPatSS3UxYA0QJvtfD91Llqt4Qjy3u5lfQjdoXi0c0ECzkcBovXQB_oVGjx_tGaoUpFKPa1ZrgXT2Yo14vTykbIPY9fya1eGpFgANz7cTP6ggZIu4KF9lUFk7n7BL2RwFoDoHF0Fyb3Tnm-U8-Wbg52Napa3Ia_byjdXzcI4pg2ZMp7vi-mnS5S8meUE3rY5fNrhOKPA9VpXCL8pMDHZknZS9KgpxCbp4p7Sjb8-XUMbVgT4EAOFltkyqpwLLdr46mcyz8vJ3-al9k6z87l5ZjSOo2LqCFLsdKogaYX_Z-xUxvlMA3ZQgxf5iaxf44OTF97zbpE2zN6SnxhrsxNHqh1rpk6Y1wwaUCu_xkIuDcMt_vkZ_rq5y39KElPKsuD1shCMO2k9cX8hT8jRNCHczDmXYAkoJFEX3g0FEHjiFGt2XC5e93w7i2Nbkj5maBWdrJEACcvjPhBWRrz_tTja/EQdYQs5yHQROFVoMA6jLVii8SvsEz091/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="马克龙的预算结局预示着法国政治更加混乱"&gt;风险最高的&lt;/a&gt;财政冲突，总理和财政部长强调遏制不断膨胀的债务负担的紧迫性。他们的请求表明，自 2024 年以来，一个因预算问题而导致两位总理下台的支离破碎的政治体系很可能在今年晚些时候引发新一轮的混乱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;一向无所不在的&lt;/strong&gt;英国改革派领导人奈杰尔·法拉奇(Nigel Farage)在遭受一系列选举挫折和个人财务受到&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/THLjEzrz-tP0nfrWGCSTvjom_wAR9_oGKPE5MNEeofcY1bo3c3Ei9PRWiOxIul7UUc-5TYGFatsUEPp3neQyAa7tLRnn5Irs4RtkkOgv5fzzO--ug4IP-1826i9Whi0nR0RiNWa8T53JxeRg43hVNTtE1oQw-A0PbnRdN6L_ENYrJY486YzF57SX-UfNX4h0KMfhBGXq8Z7VGICZ2kb-sHgm0llCpwaig7EiT3C8sTI1vdUfMgBE1GkC0GugiPW0kYVkAboUn5bjxNtg5isTb3tvNsUAQIK65obsD8I5ig3sJqyUnLxLGuZpe1Z-jpmNQ__CS1vGWDOBfU2qeL8ScbU-ruInLIpGFg4PZmfDyrL3h-rVqdA80CPA3THGQ0qUWLv-L32xIEB73xWKXQJFh-oyqUNmNKI-qgRGInlxfGHucWoV2t-Cf2lWARVZ4QEK77oyI0_7EKqjpaxD36l0FhymVTg3z5sCtTAeCFAK98LwLxva1VYqAaLmmpm9WPzqJUE1EfvgrPmfkV31FZf2rMiSUOmJ9-ghqFhYgawCvN3y/ishs5dva_U-hHrSfUKfI0ATZM2nhNts2/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着金融调查的深入，法拉奇退出视野"&gt;前所未有的审查&lt;/a&gt;后，似乎罕见地不再在英国公开露面。根据&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.